    you enter a selection command, then this auto command entry feature
    temporarily disabled. This is disabled when using a show ALL Notices

  o Print Dest:  RJE Destination or VTAM printer when P selection is use
    news item or when the REPORT primary command is used to print News S

  o Print CAPS/ASIS:  Print news item in all CAPS for printers with no l
    case capability.

